Improvements in 1.7.0
- All plist data types are now supported in table fields, adding Data, Date, custom Array, and custom Dictionary
- All table input fields now support interaction and type adapters similar to their free-standing counterparts
- Microsoft Edge's ManagedFavorites as well as both Google Chrome's and Brave's ManagedBookmarks are now fully supported thanks to new non-homogeneous array handling capabilities
